# Skills shipped to Centaur sandboxes via the overlay contract.
#
# This is the curation surface: one skill name per line, matching a
# directory under skills/. scripts/sync-sandbox-skills.sh copies each
# listed skill into .agents/skills/ (the chart's default skillsSubdir);
# CI fails if the generated tree drifts from this list.
#
# Keep this to self-contained reasoning/process skills. Skills that
# assume a workstation (macOS setup, local key material) or post to
# external services (Slack, Linear) stay out unless sandboxes gain
# those capabilities.

brainstorming
caveman-commit
definition-of-done
diagnose
handoff
receiving-code-review
repository-organization
requesting-code-review
test-driven-development
